Class FlipFitGymOwner

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitUser
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitGymOwner
public class FlipFitGymOwner extends FlipFitUser
Represents a gym owner in the FlipFit system, extending FlipFitUser. Contains owner-specific details such as PAN number, associated gym center IDs, card details, and approval status.
Author:
gamma-group
